{"tid":2363573,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"迷信po 香港支那蛇陣其實係笑話","createTime":"2021-01-12T09:55:16.000Z","updateTime":"2021-01-13T13:01:51.000Z","uid":200120,"like":2,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"c139150f1e4f9557d0314c97379ea441bc412b98","tid":2363573,"uid":200120,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-12T09:55:16.000Z","msg":"用蛇整香港人真係個風水佬On99<br />\n<br />\n古代嶺南人最撚鐘意食蟲食蛇<br />\n<br />\n到依家廣州都好撚興食蛇宴<br />\n<br />\n乜柒椒鹽蛇碌，蛇羹，炸蛇丸<br />\n<br />\n屌喇星<br />\n<br />\n搞到我每次過尖咀海傍都勁撚肚餓<br />\n<br />\n差啲咬落個欄度<br />\n<br />\n所以話有蛇陣，係真<br />\n<br />\n但話蛇陣惡，就睇你係邊種人<br />\n<br />\n驚蛇嘅，定係食蛇嘅<br />\n<br />\n老實講風水嘢最後都係講個惡字<br />\n<br />\n睇邊個食住邊個<br />\n<br />\n想年年身體健康行運行到落腳趾尾<br />\n<br />\n就喺蛇局入面食下蛇啦"},{"pid":"1ffebf7777228e726ad71ad4a2f449ccc9c00d42","tid":2363573,"uid":200120,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-12T09:57:25.000Z","msg":"老實講<br />\n<br />\n如果信風水<br />\n<br />\n咁就認真啲去相信<br />\n<br />\n做啲嘢去對抗<br />\n<br />\n一日到黑得個驚字<br />\n<br />\n真係好撚On9"},{"pid":"9e89ce609b14f87bedb112833f534bf7564eabea","tid":2363573,"uid":37719,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-12T10:24:21.000Z","msg":"其實係鬼佬起，令香港人變毒蛇咬番中國<br />\n一個有料既師傅話我知的"},{"pid":"94a0cdb54b355b405e08d4f935451f4301638529","tid":2363573,"uid":2383,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-12T10:37:45.000Z","msg":"咁幾時咬欄<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"722fc458a534295dfbf75f19fe5daacccc35fc06","tid":2363573,"uid":297119,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-12T11:01:28.000Z","msg":"咁你幾時咬欄<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ce32eb10492e0cb8968fa50200df5ca84018069b","tid":2363573,"uid":200120,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-12T11:40:53.000Z","msg":"咬咗，甩埋牙<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/slick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"16f11da79b217862fcf2129263b72079ba4d6f76","tid":2363573